Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Who's next for President?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wyjb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Feb 1983
As Reagan enters his third year, it's time to look at possible contenders for the next election. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less